Wow, the screenplay, the acting, and the voices all come from God. Everyone should see this.

The storyline and the actors did a great job in this movie.  This a movie that people can relate to especially any woman who have ever loved someone and never receives that love back.  Anyone that has been verbally abused by their partner for years until those words become a self fulfilling prophecy.  Sometimes verbal abuse that has continued for years has the same effect if not an even more powerful effect on someone's life as if that loved one have physical beat them for years.  There is a strong message of never giving up when life has knocked you down several times, perseverance, loving yourself, and shows that having even if it's just as much faith of a mustard seed will carry you through to overcome those barriers and obstacles that have held you back.  This movie teaches you that even when it seems like all hell have broke loose that your faith in God and knowing and believing in him will lead you on the right path in life.  It teaches you that even when you feel like no one is there or cares that if you cry out to God, have faith, and live your life according to his plan you will be set free on the right path.  This movie is a must have in your collection.
